Package routing.community

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Centrality
    Abstracts the concept of a centrality computation algorithm (where Centrality is defined in the context of a social network).
    CommunityDetection
    An abstraction of community detection algorithms that track and assemble a set of nodes defined to the local community of this object.
    CommunityDetectionEngine
    Declares a RoutingDecisionEngine object to also perform community detection in some fashion.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AvgDegreeCentrality
    Computes the global and local centrality of a node using the average degree centrality algorithm described in BUBBLE Rap: Social-based Forwarding in Delay Tolerant Networks by Pan Hui et al.
    CWindowCentrality
    Computes the global and local centrality of a node using the CWindow centrality algorithm described in BUBBLE Rap: Social-based Forwarding in Delay Tolerant Networks by Pan Hui et al.
    DegreeCentrality
    Computes the global and local centrality of a node using a version of the DEGREE centrality computation algorithm described in BUBBLE Rap: Social-based Forwarding in Delay Tolerant Networks by Pan Hui et al.
    DistributedBubbleRap
    Implements the Distributed BubbleRap Routing Algorithm from Hui et al.
    Duration
    A helper class for the community package that stores a start and end value for some abstract duration.
    KCliqueCommunityDetection
    Performs the K-Clique Community Detection algorithm described in Distributed Community Detection in Delay Tolerant Networks by Pan Hui et al.
    LABELDecisionEngine
    Implements the LABEL routing protocol described in How Small Labels create Big Improvements by Pan Hui and Jon Crowcroft (2007).
    ModularityCommunityDetection  
    SimpleCommunityDetection
    Performs the SIMPLE Community Detection algorithm described in Distributed Community Detection in Delay Tolerant Networks by Pan Hui et al.
    SWindowCentrality
    Computes the centrality of a node using the SWindow centrality algorithm described in BUBBLE Rap: Social-based Forwarding in Delay Tolerant Networks by Pan Hui et al.
